text: Aizpuru is a surname. Notable people with the surname include: *Juana de Aizpuru (born 1933), Spanish art gallerist *Julián Elorza Aizpuru (1879–1964), Spanish politician *Manuela Sáenz y Aizpuru (1797–1856), Ecuadorian revolutionary *Pilar Gonzalbo Aizpuru (born 1935), Spanish academic
